✓ DESCRIPTION
Bitcoin Classic (BCX) is a Solana-based token designed to integrate Bitcoin’s strengths, such as limited supply and decentralization, with the high transaction speeds and low fees of the Solana blockchain. It serves as an efficient digital payment tool, a store of value, and a utility asset within the DeFi ecosystem. With a maximum supply of 21 million tokens inspired by Bitcoin, BCX offers scalability for daily transactions and long-term value potential. It provides a modern alternative for users seeking stability, functionality, and optimal network performance.

✓ KEY FEATURES
  • Transaction Speed : Utilizes Solana’s technology to process thousands of transactions per second.
  • Low Fees          : Offers significantly reduced transaction fees compared to other blockchains.
  • Interoperability  : Compatible with SPL wallets like Phantom and Sollet, and integrable into DeFi applications within the Solana ecosystem.
  • Limited Supply    : Capped at 21 million BCX to ensure scarcity and support long-term value potential.

✓ USE CASES
  • A tool for cross-border peer-to-peer payments with low fees.
  • A digital store of value as an alternative to Bitcoin on a faster network.
  • Use in staking mechanisms or liquidity provision on Solana-based DeFi platforms.
  • A digital investment asset with potential value appreciation due to its limited supply.
